messages.message:
I can again reproduce the blank page issue when visiting aihub-sandbox. It fetches the scripts from memory cache (didn't do hard reload), but the integrity attribute does not match.
When diffing the server responded scripts in incognito, I can see some minor differences, but the version number is the same.
`monaco.bundle.js?v=1698346704.0491111`

```Failed to find a valid digest in the 'integrity' attribute for resource 'https://aihub-sandbox.internal.instabase.com/static/output/ibapp_aihub.bundle.js?v=1698346704.0491111' with computed SHA-256 integrity 'zmWjqmJy3whOZ9GW2oTUiQOc1FVGeJjOZ3wTP6GiFf4='. The resource has been blocked.```
